        <footnote id="F1">On December 19, 2018, the reporting person had 1,936 shares withheld and cancelled to cover minimum required tax withholdings due to the vesting of performance shares. These share cancellations are shown on Table I as dispositions (Transaction Code &quot;D&quot; in Column 4), although none of these cancelled shares were sold into the market, as indicated by Transaction Code &quot;F&quot; in Column 3.</footnote>
